He is the 2002 [[United States Figure Skating Championships|U.S. junior silver medalist]] and 2000 novice national champion. He is the 2009 [[Finlandia Trophy]] silver medalist and the 2007 [[Nebelhorn Trophy]] silver medalist. Shaun currently skates on board [[Royal Caribbean Cruise Lines]]. ==Competitive highlights== {| class="wikitable" |- !
